{"type":"message","id":"b60fa8a7","parentId":"23dcd9c0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:27:19.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有最近5分钟的用户消息。但等等，我需要考虑机器人的消息。我应该查询机器人（我）收到的消息，而不是用户发出的消息。\n\n让我换一种方式：查询与机器人的对话。但我不知道chat_id，让我尝试搜索消息。实际上，我应该检查的是：是否有用户发给机器人的消息（最近的）。\n\n让我试试用飞书IM搜索最近5分钟内的消息。","thinkingSignature":"0c4a0d34e6be2cda9b3332c0bb9d6bac72e0d5207c6c2eab9c8618b87431351b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8pk0prho8psj_1","name":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","arguments":{"relative_time":"last_5_minutes","page_size":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":5330,"output":122,"cacheRead":33506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38958,"cost":{"input":0.001599,"output":0.00014639999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0010051799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00275058}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774006036032}}
{"type":"message","id":"5312ccde","parentId":"b60fa8a7","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:27:20.786Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8pk0prho8psj_1","toolName":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6a11b70a8c38e7bf18cacdc3\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"需要你人工在开放平台配置。审批事件暂时无法监听，可以先实现发起审批\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_f04668d51f633318ccb47375b7b2ba10\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:26:53+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"thread_id\": \"omt_1ad898956f8e5cbc\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_21827e7a25f848f3527d1e5ead4bed39\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6a48c90a4c4d7b577af3295b\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"<p>https://open.larkoffice.com/document/common-capabilities/applink-protocol/supported-protocol/open-scan-function 可以要求妙搭生成 https://applink.feishu.cn/client/qrcode/main  链接来触发</p>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_f04668d51f633318ccb47375b7b2ba10\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:25:24+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"thread_id\": \"omt_1ad8adf6504d5b95\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_21827e7a25f848f3527d1e5ead4bed39\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6ab7df0a0b4bd4bfe268dda7\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card>\\n您好呀～目前飞书x Openclaw的限时免费活动与您提到的“微信免费4K万token每天”政策不符哦～\\n当前妙搭推出的**限时免费创建OpenClaw活动**中，所有已注册的妙搭用户可享受的免费额度为：\\n- **首日发放400万Tokens**，后续每日发放**100万Tokens**\\n- 活动时间：截至2026年3月31日24:00（北京时间）\\n**补充说明：**\\n- 每日额度将于当日00:00（北京时间）自动发放，**仅限当日有效**，未使用部分不累计至次日；\\n- 若当日免费额度用尽，个人用户可购买[飞书AI高级会员](https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/234159142166-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A9%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E9%A3%9E%E4%B9%A6-ai-%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E4%BC%9A%E5%91%98)